      "type": "Title",
      "text": "5.2 Narrative",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 95,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "We expect revenue growth to moderate as the consumer environment normalizes but remain positive across all segments.",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Operating margin is expected to be broadly stable as gross margin improvements are offset by continued wage and technology investments.",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Capex will increase to support store remodels, fulfillment capacity, and core systems modernization.",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 98,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Key priorities for FY2025:",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Improve Marketplace unit economics, especially returns and customer service costs;",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Maintain inventory discipline to avoid excess markdowns;",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Execute the first wave of store remodels on time and on budget.",
      "section_path": "5.2 Narrative"
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "page": null,
      "type": "Title",
      "text": "5.3 Risks and opportunities",
      "section_path": "5.3 Risks and opportunities"
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Upside:",
      "section_path": "5.3 Risks and opportunities"
    },
    {
      "id": 104,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "If Marketplace growth remains above 30% and we improve contribution margins, there is upside to profitability.",
      "section_path": "5.3 Risks and opportunities"
    },
    {
      "id": 105,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Downside:",
      "section_path": "5.3 Risks and opportunities"
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "A deeper consumer downturn or elevated promotional activity from competitors could pressure both revenue and margin.",
      "section_path": "5.3 Risks and opportunities"
    }
  ]
